<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> tirumakaḷ pO
<lb n="2" break="no"/>lapperunilac celviyum
<lb n="3"/>taṉakkē Urimai pūṇṭamai ma
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṉakkoḷa kāntaḷūr cālai kalama
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṟuttaruḷi vēṅkai nāṭum kaṅka
<lb n="6" break="no"/>pāṭiyum nuḷampa pāṭiyum taṭikai
<lb n="7"/>vaḻiyum kuṭamalai nāṭum kol<unclear>la</unclear>
<lb n="8" break="no"/>mum kaliṅ<supplied reason="omitted">ka</supplied>mum tiṇṭiṟal veṉṟi
<lb n="9"/>taṇṭāṟ koṇṭa taṉneḻil vaḷa
<lb n="10" break="no"/>r Ūḻiuḷ Ellāyāṇṭil toḻuta kai vi
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ḷaṅkum yāṇṭē ceḻiyarait tēcu
<lb n="12" break="no"/>koḷ kōvirā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi> rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi> kēcari <hi rend="grantha">panma</hi>kku yāṇ
<lb n="13"/>ṭu <num value="16"><g type="numeral">10</g> 6</num> tu vaṭakarai kuṟukkai nāṭṭu pirama
<lb n="14" break="no"/>tēyam viṭēl viṭukutēvi catu<hi rend="grantha">rvve</hi>tip
<lb n="15"/>pāl tirumaṇañcēri Iṉiteḻuntaruḷi Irun
<lb n="16" break="no"/>ta maṇavāḷa perumāḷukku Innāṭṭu Am
<lb n="17" break="no"/>par Ampar Uṭaiyāṉ māṟantiṭṭai vait
<lb n="18" break="no"/>ta nontāviḷakku 1 Itinukku cāvā mūvāp
<lb n="19" break="no"/>pērrāṭu toṇṇūṟṟāṟu Ivai
<lb n="20"/><hi rend="grantha">panmāheśvara rakṣai</hi> 
</p>

